  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess various published staging tools to assess the health impacts of&#xD;
      obesity on individuals. The aim is to identify benefits and drawbacks, and thus help Obesity&#xD;
      Centres and GPs better assess obese individuals as well as better identify who benefits most&#xD;
      from having weight loss treatment.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess various published staging tools to assess the health impacts of&#xD;
      obesity on individuals. The aim is to identify benefits and drawbacks, and thus help Obesity&#xD;
      Centres and GPs better assess obese individuals as well as better identify who benefits most&#xD;
      from having weight loss treatment&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
